The '''Seeker Rail Detonator''' was a [[Rail detonator]] which used [[Seeking rail charge]]s. Its only known difference from a regular Rail Detonator was an ability to fire rail charges which would follow the nearest enemy until it hit. Apart from this ability, it was presumably an identical weapon.

